com.poesys.db.dao

Class MessagingDaoManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.poesys.db.dao.CacheDaoManager
      • com.poesys.db.dao.MessagingDaoManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDaoManager

    public final class MessagingDaoManager
extends CacheDaoManager
implements IDaoManager
    A singleton object that manages data access objects in the system. The manager maintains a singleton map of caches which is available on demand and message-handling for the JMS PoesysCacheDelete messaging topic, which enables clustered node cache object removal. This implementation of DAO Manager returns the same DAO factory singleton as the CacheDaoManager.
    Author:
    Robert J. Muller
    See Also:
    CacheDaoManager
